WEBVTT

00:13.830 --> 00:14.800
Your Majesty!

00:17.000 --> 00:17.800
Your Majesty!

00:18.480 --> 00:22.000
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

00:22.670 --> 00:23.760
Your Majesty!

00:24.670 --> 00:25.550
Your Majesty!

00:25.830 --> 00:27.560
-Your Majesty!
-Your Majesty!

00:28.190 --> 00:28.990
General Huan,

00:29.190 --> 00:30.990
we found no trace of His Majesty.

00:32.470 --> 00:33.750
Your Majesty!

00:42.350 --> 00:43.240
Your Majesty!

00:44.670 --> 00:45.600
General Huan!

00:50.750 --> 00:51.560
Your Majesty!

02:22.900 --> 02:27.650
[Rebirth]

02:28.140 --> 02:30.690
[Episode 4]

02:52.120 --> 02:53.180
It's hypothermia.

02:53.520 --> 02:56.590
Qianzhang Lake has been frozen for years.

02:57.150 --> 03:00.030
The cold has invaded his internal organs.

03:00.400 --> 03:04.840
Ordinary people
cannot withstand hypothermia.

03:10.960 --> 03:11.750
Summon the imperial physician!

03:11.750 --> 03:12.360
Yes!

03:13.750 --> 03:15.310
Lock down the itinerant court!

03:15.310 --> 03:16.840
Search the area around Qianzhang Lake!

03:16.840 --> 03:17.960
Find Chu Qiao for me—

03:17.960 --> 03:19.400
no matter whether dead or alive!

03:19.400 --> 03:20.060
-Yes!
-Yes!

03:28.630 --> 03:31.030
You've been checking his pulse
for an hour.

03:31.120 --> 03:32.150
How is he?

03:35.190 --> 03:36.520
G-General Cheng.

03:37.190 --> 03:40.400
Although His Majesty's wound is not fatal,

03:40.680 --> 03:42.310
it is close to the heart.

03:42.470 --> 03:43.680
Coupled with falling into the lake

03:43.680 --> 03:46.079
which caused the extreme cold
to invade his organs,

03:46.079 --> 03:48.240
all his internal organs have...

03:49.520 --> 03:51.320
Are you saying he can't be saved?

03:51.710 --> 03:53.150
He can.

03:53.840 --> 03:56.150
But he needs the protection of the gods.

03:56.450 --> 03:58.400
I am only a mortal.

03:58.430 --> 04:01.390
The medicine I practice
can only alleviate pain.

04:01.560 --> 04:02.470
But I cannot...

04:03.470 --> 04:05.870
alter fate.

04:11.390 --> 04:13.870
[Ximeng, the border of Great Yan]

04:23.040 --> 04:25.700
This is the border
between Ximeng and Great Yan.

04:25.830 --> 04:27.530
They can't return
to Great Yan or Great Yong.

04:27.530 --> 04:29.330
They must be hiding in this area.

04:30.310 --> 04:31.800
Search carefully.

04:32.750 --> 04:34.680
If we can't bring this person back,

04:35.070 --> 04:36.240
we will all die.

04:35.830 --> 04:37.580
[Ximeng Lingyue Clan's
Queen of Lingyue]

04:37.000 --> 04:37.659
-Yes!
-Yes!

04:38.000 --> 04:39.310
That cave ahead.

04:39.870 --> 04:41.000
You few, follow me.

04:41.070 --> 04:43.070
The rest of you, block the cave.

04:43.240 --> 04:44.300
If you find anyone,

04:44.800 --> 04:46.360
don't let them escape.

04:46.360 --> 04:47.390
-Yes!
-Yes!

04:58.280 --> 04:58.940
Don't move.

05:04.430 --> 05:06.030
Take me to the King of Ximeng.

05:06.870 --> 05:07.870
It's been 3 days.

05:08.070 --> 05:09.830
There's still no news of His Majesty.

05:09.830 --> 05:11.680
We need to go and see

05:11.750 --> 05:13.000
what exactly is going on.

05:13.000 --> 05:16.790
-We want to see His Majesty!
-We want to see His Majesty!

05:16.810 --> 05:17.750
General Cheng has ordered that

05:17.750 --> 05:18.920
His Majesty is unwell

05:18.920 --> 05:20.120
and needs to rest and recover.

05:20.120 --> 05:20.980
General Cheng?

05:22.190 --> 05:23.650
General Cheng is nothing.

05:23.650 --> 05:24.650
Get out of the way!

05:24.800 --> 05:25.680
Get out of the way!

05:25.680 --> 05:26.800
You can't enter!

05:27.030 --> 05:27.830
You can't go in!

05:27.830 --> 05:28.490
Step aside!

05:29.680 --> 05:31.140
We want to see His Majesty!

05:31.600 --> 05:32.260
Step aside!

05:32.870 --> 05:33.800
You can't enter.

05:45.920 --> 05:47.310
Lord Tumu, let it go.

05:48.000 --> 05:50.270
General Cheng's men
are guarding the bedchamber.

05:50.270 --> 05:51.240
Going there now

05:51.240 --> 05:52.270
won't do you any good.

05:52.270 --> 05:53.830
Are we supposed to just wait?

05:53.830 --> 05:55.159
A country cannot go a day without a king.

05:55.159 --> 05:56.510
We need to know

05:56.750 --> 05:58.750
whether His Majesty is in danger or not!

05:58.750 --> 06:00.190
Now, all the imperial doctors

06:00.190 --> 06:02.750
have been locked in the bedchamber
by Cheng Yuan,

06:02.750 --> 06:04.070
not allowed to leave.

06:04.600 --> 06:06.660
What exactly are they hiding from us?

06:07.160 --> 06:08.760
There are too many ears here.

06:08.800 --> 06:10.480
You must speak carefully, my lord.

06:10.480 --> 06:11.540
What am I afraid of?

06:12.000 --> 06:13.070
Do you know

06:13.360 --> 06:15.870
that in recent days,
Cheng Yuan led his men

06:15.870 --> 06:18.800
to destroy several strongholds
of the Universal Harmony Guild?

06:18.800 --> 06:21.270
He mobilized his Black Eagle Army

06:21.870 --> 06:23.630
to the surroundings
of the Capital of Great Yan.

06:23.630 --> 06:24.430
Are you saying

06:24.830 --> 06:26.720
Cheng Yuan has brought his troops
to the Capital of Great Yan?

06:26.720 --> 06:29.310
General Cheng used the excuse
of providing protection,

06:29.310 --> 06:32.640
saying he was worried about chaos
occurring in the capital.

06:36.159 --> 06:38.420
I think the first person to cause trouble

06:38.600 --> 06:39.950
in the capital

06:39.950 --> 06:41.120
would be Cheng Yuan.

06:41.390 --> 06:42.790
You exaggerate, My Lord.

06:42.920 --> 06:45.310
Lord Tumu must be talking about me.

06:46.310 --> 06:46.830
Well...

07:00.720 --> 07:01.680
Lord Huo Sang.

07:03.170 --> 07:03.970
General Shi.

07:05.480 --> 07:06.390
Lord Tumu.

07:10.390 --> 07:12.120
You guys are in high spirits.

07:16.040 --> 07:18.160
May I ask why you are trespassing

07:18.680 --> 07:19.580
on the royal palace?

07:19.580 --> 07:22.230
I should be asking you that, Lord Cheng.

07:22.310 --> 07:24.560
You deployed troops to seal off
the itinerant court without authorization,

07:24.560 --> 07:25.970
and confined His Majesty.

07:25.970 --> 07:26.970
What are you up to?

07:30.390 --> 07:32.050
His Majesty is safe and sound.

07:32.390 --> 07:34.630
He'll attend the court soon.

07:34.920 --> 07:37.070
Word came out of the court yesterday

07:37.870 --> 07:39.200
that His Majesty is ill—

07:47.480 --> 07:49.240
His Majesty just caught a cold.

07:49.460 --> 07:51.260
He is resting in his bedchamber.

07:53.890 --> 07:56.520
He'll recover soon.

07:57.360 --> 07:58.950
To prevent any accident
in the Capital of Great Yan,

07:58.950 --> 08:00.390
I will inform General Huan

08:00.390 --> 08:02.270
to preside over

08:02.270 --> 08:04.430
the capital's security matters with me.

08:04.430 --> 08:05.630
From today on,

08:06.360 --> 08:09.120
anyone who spreads rumors
about His Majesty being ill

08:09.120 --> 08:10.590
and dampens public morale

08:11.870 --> 08:14.270
will not be forgiven.

08:32.150 --> 08:34.210
I want the medicine for hypothermia.

08:41.030 --> 08:42.549
The medicine is here.

08:42.770 --> 08:44.370
What do you have in exchange?

08:55.030 --> 08:57.240
Now, what do you have in exchange?

08:58.840 --> 09:00.370
If you hesitate any longer,

09:00.600 --> 09:02.270
the woman in the cave

09:02.270 --> 09:05.120
will lose her only chance to live.

09:13.710 --> 09:15.160
I'll trade my life for it.

09:17.150 --> 09:19.360
This is a secret poison of Ximeng.

09:19.460 --> 09:21.790
You'll become
a living dead if you eat it.

09:22.550 --> 09:24.720
Be it General Zhuge of Great Yong

09:24.840 --> 09:27.440
or the manager
of Great Yong's Qingshan Manor—

09:27.670 --> 09:29.600
they are all dead.

09:29.600 --> 09:31.270
I've been dead for a long time.

10:11.630 --> 10:13.390
Didn't you want to walk for them?

10:13.390 --> 10:14.360
Stand up.

10:14.520 --> 10:15.360
Keep walking!

10:17.840 --> 10:18.630
Young Master Huai.

10:18.630 --> 10:19.630
Young Master Huai, please forgive Xiaoliu.

10:19.630 --> 10:20.630
Young Master Huai, please forgive Xiaoliu.

10:20.630 --> 10:22.620
-Young Master Huai, please spare her.
-Go!

10:22.620 --> 10:23.680
Young Master Huai.

10:30.200 --> 10:31.160
Are you walking or not?

10:31.160 --> 10:33.160
If you don't, I'll beat her to death.

10:40.240 --> 10:41.500
Are you walking or not?

10:42.390 --> 10:43.270
Stop beating!

10:44.230 --> 10:45.920
I'll walk. I'll walk.

11:19.670 --> 11:20.550
Zhuge Yue?

11:20.670 --> 11:21.730
What are you doing?

11:27.360 --> 11:27.960
You,

11:28.670 --> 11:29.750
what's your name?

12:17.800 --> 12:19.630
This is the wound medicine
Young Master Yue rewarded you with.

12:19.630 --> 12:20.490
Use it quickly.

13:07.420 --> 13:11.040
♪ The dust in the world ♪

13:11.420 --> 13:14.890
♪ Is blown away easily by the wind ♪

13:15.740 --> 13:18.540
♪ Who can stay calm ♪

13:19.300 --> 13:20.650
♪ And not be scared? ♪

13:20.750 --> 13:22.760
♪ A slight ripple ♪

13:23.120 --> 13:25.670
♪ We face ♪

13:25.690 --> 13:29.550
♪ The heavy thunderstorm together ♪

13:30.700 --> 13:33.430
♪ Even with extreme pain ♪

13:33.460 --> 13:38.230
♪ We don't even wince ♪

13:38.540 --> 13:42.300
♪ No matter how a jade is carved ♪

13:42.330 --> 13:46.550
♪ It's just a stone ♪

13:46.850 --> 13:53.130
♪ It will eventually disappear ♪

13:56.600 --> 13:57.960
Stay in Qingshan Manor.

13:58.630 --> 13:59.290
From now on,

14:00.270 --> 14:01.550
your name is Xing.

14:32.040 --> 14:34.950
♪ We mock karma ♪

14:35.880 --> 14:38.460
♪ For being unfair ♪

14:38.880 --> 14:40.860
♪ Why is life ♪

14:41.110 --> 14:45.160
♪ Often filled with regrets? ♪

14:43.960 --> 14:44.630
Xing.

14:46.390 --> 14:47.000
Here.

14:46.930 --> 14:49.370
♪ The snow falls ♪

14:48.120 --> 14:49.180
Take the medicine.

14:49.780 --> 14:52.950
♪ With fate ♪

14:53.790 --> 14:55.030
♪ It will eventually ♪

14:55.480 --> 14:57.480
♪ Fall before ♪

14:57.500 --> 14:59.960
♪ The dawn ♪

15:00.440 --> 15:02.650
♪ As a foreigner ♪

15:02.820 --> 15:07.370
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

15:07.660 --> 15:09.930
♪ Wander ♪

15:10.150 --> 15:14.360
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

15:14.840 --> 15:17.080
♪ The lock in my heart ♪

15:17.280 --> 15:18.710
♪ Put the memories ♪

15:18.740 --> 15:22.610
♪ In the silence of the night ♪

15:23.070 --> 15:24.370
♪ Look ♪

15:24.690 --> 15:28.830
♪ The mortal world has forgotten me ♪

15:30.410 --> 15:31.480
♪ I wish ♪

15:32.390 --> 15:41.530
♪ You'll forget me ♪

15:47.910 --> 15:49.120
Zhuge Yue, don't go.

15:49.750 --> 15:50.390
Xing.

15:51.270 --> 15:51.910
Xing.

15:53.600 --> 15:54.840
Don't leave me alone.

15:55.320 --> 15:56.630
Don't leave me alone.

15:56.790 --> 15:57.750
Zhuge Yue.

15:59.270 --> 16:01.000
I won't let you go again.

16:12.530 --> 16:14.170
This is Blood on Snow.

16:14.360 --> 16:16.820
It's refined from a flower
unique to Ximeng.

16:17.000 --> 16:18.240
Once taken,

16:18.240 --> 16:20.600
one will be dependent on it constantly.

16:21.480 --> 16:24.270
I gave you a 10-day dose,

16:24.600 --> 16:27.060
enough for you to go back
and save your woman.

16:27.200 --> 16:28.360
But after 10 days,

16:28.360 --> 16:30.200
if you don't return as promised,

16:30.910 --> 16:32.390
I'll let you know

16:32.390 --> 16:34.840
what a living hell is.

17:00.080 --> 17:02.210
The King of Ximeng promised me 10 days.

17:02.670 --> 17:04.800
But you've already come in such a hurry

17:05.000 --> 17:06.599
when only 7 days have passed?

17:09.589 --> 17:11.960
It takes 3 days
to get from here to Ximeng City.

17:11.960 --> 17:13.109
Only with our escort

17:13.109 --> 17:15.200
can we ensure
you won't suffer from Blood on Snow

17:15.200 --> 17:17.550
and that you survive intact.

17:19.790 --> 17:21.680
With your poor martial arts,

17:22.030 --> 17:23.880
you say you can escort me?

17:24.200 --> 17:26.550
Besides, I'm already a walking corpse.

17:35.120 --> 17:36.380
You're no match for me.

17:37.480 --> 17:39.440
I won't make things difficult for you.

17:39.440 --> 17:40.680
I'll go with you.

18:44.850 --> 18:45.440
Stop.

18:48.130 --> 18:48.930
-Go.
-Go.

18:50.490 --> 18:51.100
Go.

18:57.830 --> 18:58.790
Take a look!

19:00.770 --> 19:01.730
Your noodles.

19:02.060 --> 19:02.990
Enjoy your meal.

19:03.510 --> 19:04.200
Sir.

19:04.790 --> 19:06.450
I'd like to ask you something.

19:06.600 --> 19:07.270
Go ahead.

19:07.310 --> 19:08.920
It's chaotic out there.

19:08.960 --> 19:10.030
There are so many soldiers too.

19:10.030 --> 19:11.030
What happened?

19:11.030 --> 19:11.440
You...

19:12.200 --> 19:13.350
You don't know yet?

19:14.160 --> 19:16.760
There's been a big chaos
in Great Yan recently.

19:17.960 --> 19:18.790
What happened?

19:18.790 --> 19:19.720
We commoners

19:19.720 --> 19:21.550
don't know exactly what's going on.

19:21.550 --> 19:22.610
But in recent days,

19:22.680 --> 19:24.310
many places in Great Yan's towns

19:24.310 --> 19:26.200
have been surrounded and suppressed
by the Black Eagle Army.

19:26.200 --> 19:27.920
It's said they are arresting

19:27.920 --> 19:30.120
rebels of the Universal Harmony Guild.

19:30.240 --> 19:31.200
I heard

19:31.350 --> 19:34.240
that the Universal Harmony Guild
laid an ambush on Mount Ximin

19:34.240 --> 19:35.400
with the intention of rebelling,

19:35.400 --> 19:36.830
and everyone was killed.

19:37.400 --> 19:39.460
Was this an order from the King of Yan?

19:39.610 --> 19:40.350
No.

19:41.270 --> 19:42.730
It was General Cheng Yuan.

19:43.110 --> 19:43.960
Don't you know?

19:43.960 --> 19:45.000
His Majesty is sick.

19:45.000 --> 19:46.830
The imperial doctors
in the palace can't cure him.

19:46.830 --> 19:48.750
They are looking for civilian doctors
all over Great Yan to enter the palace

19:48.750 --> 19:49.950
to treat His Majesty.

19:51.070 --> 19:52.240
Go, hurry up!

19:52.720 --> 19:53.200
Go!

19:55.270 --> 19:55.920
Go!

19:57.630 --> 19:58.460
It looks like

19:58.710 --> 20:01.840
this is another rebel
from the Universal Harmony Guild.

20:18.810 --> 20:21.000
Can this person survive hanging like this?

20:21.000 --> 20:22.400
What do you mean survive?

20:22.470 --> 20:23.840
She's from the Universal Harmony Guild.

20:23.840 --> 20:25.230
They won't let her live.

20:25.590 --> 20:27.830
With people of the Universal Harmony Guild
all dead,

20:27.830 --> 20:30.630
life in Great Yan
will be even harder in the future.

20:35.160 --> 20:37.240
I heard that not only
the Universal Harmony Guild,

20:37.240 --> 20:39.400
but also the Xiuli Army dying out
at Meilin Pass

20:39.400 --> 20:41.000
was General Cheng's doing.

20:41.350 --> 20:43.400
It was 5,000 Xiuli soldiers
against 100,000 Yong soldiers.

20:43.400 --> 20:44.310
They were abandoned.

20:44.310 --> 20:45.640
How could they survive?

20:45.750 --> 20:47.310
Their corpses
were thrown into the mass grave,

20:47.310 --> 20:48.840
with no one to care for them.

20:54.880 --> 20:55.550
He Xiao...

20:57.200 --> 20:58.130
Commander Chen.

21:01.270 --> 21:02.310
Where are you?

21:06.440 --> 21:08.400
He Xiao!

21:13.190 --> 21:14.670
Did I do something wrong?

21:14.880 --> 21:16.310
Come out!

21:17.440 --> 21:19.480
He Xiao, Commander Chen!

21:19.790 --> 21:20.790
Come out!

21:21.030 --> 21:23.070
I want you alive!

22:50.960 --> 22:52.000
I expected that

22:52.200 --> 22:54.660
the Queen is a person
who values friendship.

22:54.920 --> 22:56.720
Even at the cost of your own life,

22:57.350 --> 22:59.510
you would come to save
your former comrades.

22:59.510 --> 23:00.170
Therefore,

23:01.200 --> 23:03.510
I have been waiting here for a long time.

23:04.440 --> 23:07.070
General Cheng and I were also comrades.

23:07.830 --> 23:08.960
Unfortunately,

23:09.680 --> 23:11.140
now we can only be enemies.

23:14.590 --> 23:15.390
Go after them!

23:32.790 --> 23:33.510
Miss Zhong!

23:39.510 --> 23:40.270
Miss Zhong.

23:43.920 --> 23:44.720
Hang in there.

23:45.160 --> 23:46.830
Go, leave me.

23:54.160 --> 23:55.620
Let's jump into the river.

23:59.570 --> 24:00.510
Kill them!

24:12.680 --> 24:13.400
Chu Qiao.

24:14.750 --> 24:16.640
Today is your death day.

24:44.590 --> 24:45.440
Miss Zhong!

25:30.200 --> 25:30.960
Chu Qiao.

25:31.790 --> 25:33.000
You must die.

25:33.880 --> 25:35.160
For you,

25:35.590 --> 25:37.850
Yan Xun repeatedly abandoned Great Yan.

25:37.960 --> 25:38.920
If you don't die,

25:39.200 --> 25:41.200
the hatred of the people of Great Yan

25:41.240 --> 25:42.510
and Yan Xun's hatred

25:43.350 --> 25:45.720
will never be avenged.

25:49.620 --> 25:50.680
Live on!

25:55.310 --> 25:57.160
Zhong Yu!

27:17.680 --> 27:18.680
Miss Zhong.

27:19.350 --> 27:20.350
Miss Zhong.

27:23.310 --> 27:24.350
Zhong Yu!

27:26.270 --> 27:27.640
Zhong Yu, where are you?

27:28.310 --> 27:29.920
Zhong Yu!

27:43.680 --> 27:44.240
General,

27:44.240 --> 27:45.590
we still haven't found Chu Qiao.

27:45.590 --> 27:46.900
She is crippled now.

27:47.000 --> 27:47.920
She can't run far.

27:47.920 --> 27:49.110
Assemble the nearby Black Eagle Army.

27:49.110 --> 27:51.240
Search all villages along the valley.

27:51.270 --> 27:52.400
Even if you have to search every inch,

27:52.400 --> 27:53.590
you must find her.

27:53.590 --> 27:54.320
Understood.

27:57.800 --> 28:00.040
[Arrest]

27:59.240 --> 28:00.510
Come take a look, everyone.

28:00.510 --> 28:01.720
If you have seen this woman,

28:01.720 --> 28:02.790
report it immediately.

28:02.790 --> 28:04.120
There is a hefty reward.

28:04.520 --> 28:05.120
Sir,

28:05.590 --> 28:06.720
what happened now?

28:07.000 --> 28:07.750
Don't you know?

28:07.750 --> 28:08.960
I just came from the east.

28:08.960 --> 28:09.890
It seems they are

28:09.920 --> 28:12.350
catching the rebels
of the Universal Harmony Guild.

28:12.350 --> 28:13.720
They have been catching them
for so many days,

28:13.720 --> 28:14.830
and they still haven't caught them all?

28:14.830 --> 28:15.920
Who knows?

28:16.070 --> 28:16.680
Gentlemen.

28:16.680 --> 28:17.940
Here are your noodles.

28:21.400 --> 28:22.350
There are 2 more days.

28:22.350 --> 28:23.610
I will be back in 2 days.

28:28.120 --> 28:28.830
Follow him closely.

28:28.830 --> 28:29.350
Yes.

28:44.070 --> 28:45.160
Have mercy.

28:45.510 --> 28:46.720
Have mercy.

28:46.720 --> 28:47.880
Please give me some food.

28:47.880 --> 28:49.110
Have mercy.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.640
Listen up, everyone.

28:50.720 --> 28:51.650
Starting today,

28:52.000 --> 28:54.240
anyone leaving the city gates
must be inspected.

28:54.240 --> 28:55.570
Make things easy for us,

28:55.640 --> 28:57.040
and don't cause trouble.

28:57.240 --> 28:58.000
Search them!

28:59.070 --> 29:00.670
Look at the people over here.

29:04.110 --> 29:05.110
Have you seen this woman?

29:05.110 --> 29:06.240
N-N-No.

29:06.880 --> 29:07.880
Have you seen her?

29:07.960 --> 29:09.020
I haven't seen her.

29:45.640 --> 29:46.300
Stop there.

29:48.680 --> 29:49.720
Turn around.

29:54.030 --> 29:55.640
I said turn around.

29:55.920 --> 29:56.920
Can't you hear me?

30:17.270 --> 30:19.450
[Crown Prince of Biantang,
Li Ce]

30:20.550 --> 30:22.000
You stinky beggar.

30:22.400 --> 30:24.600
You ran away after dirtying my clothes.

30:24.750 --> 30:26.110
I'm so unlucky.

30:26.270 --> 30:27.440
Why did I have to come to

30:27.440 --> 30:27.960
this barbaric place

30:27.960 --> 30:29.720
full of beggars?

30:29.960 --> 30:30.690
Come with me.

30:30.760 --> 30:32.490
See how I'll teach you a lesson.

30:35.240 --> 30:36.570
Looking at his clothes,

30:37.110 --> 30:38.240
he's from Biantang.

30:38.550 --> 30:39.960
He's neither masculine nor feminine—

30:39.960 --> 30:41.200
smelling like fragrance powder.

30:41.200 --> 30:43.270
He's wearing a royal tablet.

30:43.680 --> 30:44.480
Could it be...

30:44.590 --> 30:45.450
Keep checking.

30:47.040 --> 30:48.040
You, stop.

30:48.270 --> 30:49.350
Stinky beggar,

30:49.350 --> 30:50.510
how dare you dirty my clothes.

30:50.510 --> 30:52.240
See how I'll teach you a lesson.

30:52.790 --> 30:53.350
Get on!

30:53.370 --> 30:53.810
Hurry.

30:55.120 --> 30:55.750
Hurry up.

30:58.000 --> 30:58.480
Get in.

31:12.680 --> 31:13.270
Qiao.

31:13.590 --> 31:14.520
Long time no see.

31:14.790 --> 31:15.720
To be honest,

31:15.960 --> 31:17.350
my travel out this time

31:17.640 --> 31:19.300
felt different from the past.

31:19.440 --> 31:21.190
I felt refreshed along the way

31:21.210 --> 31:22.600
and that good things are coming.

31:22.600 --> 31:24.280
I just arrived in Great Yan,

31:24.400 --> 31:25.750
and among the flowers,

31:26.590 --> 31:27.550
I met you.

31:28.160 --> 31:28.830
Tell me,

31:29.350 --> 31:30.310
would you call this

31:30.310 --> 31:32.550
fate bringing us together again?

31:33.400 --> 31:34.960
What's wrong with
this Crown Prince of Biantang?

31:34.960 --> 31:36.200
He said men stink

31:36.230 --> 31:38.350
and insisted on having beautiful women
to welcome him.

31:38.350 --> 31:38.830
How...

31:39.350 --> 31:41.400
How did th-this dead tree bloom?

31:42.160 --> 31:43.310
A dead tree blooming—

31:43.310 --> 31:44.310
that's an ominous sign.

31:44.310 --> 31:45.510
It's an ominous sign.

31:45.680 --> 31:46.750
This is so unlucky.

31:46.750 --> 31:47.810
Shut up, all of you.

31:48.270 --> 31:50.850
A dead tree blooming
is a rare sight in a century.

31:50.850 --> 31:52.980
It means that only those with perseverance

31:52.980 --> 31:55.840
can bloom like a dead tree
in desperate situations.

32:04.400 --> 32:05.930
Zhao Che is quite sensible,

32:06.030 --> 32:08.560
arranging such
a cute welcoming envoy for me.

32:18.750 --> 32:20.150
Welcome, Your Highness.

32:20.480 --> 32:22.510
Please follow me into the city.

32:22.830 --> 32:23.720
Beauty, come up

32:24.070 --> 32:25.440
and sit in the carriage with me,

32:25.440 --> 32:27.440
then I will follow you into the city.

32:32.590 --> 32:33.270
Go.

32:34.920 --> 32:36.600
Your Highness!

32:41.480 --> 32:43.680
There is no absolute beauty in history;

32:43.880 --> 32:46.340
one pleasing to the eye
is a beautiful woman.

32:58.790 --> 32:59.640
Your Highness!

32:59.640 --> 33:00.830
How dare you!

33:00.830 --> 33:03.360
How dare you
hit the Crown Prince of Biantang!

33:05.200 --> 33:06.330
That's even better.

33:07.380 --> 33:08.010
Chu Qiao.

33:08.920 --> 33:09.680
How dare you!

33:09.960 --> 33:10.880
Kneel down.

33:12.830 --> 33:14.030
Why are you so fierce?

33:14.160 --> 33:15.360
Do you know who she is?

33:15.680 --> 33:17.110
She is my future wife.

33:17.310 --> 33:18.830
I have seen many beautiful women,

33:18.830 --> 33:20.110
but it's my first time seeing

33:20.110 --> 33:21.310
such a fierce and violent one.

33:21.310 --> 33:22.160
Beauty, how old are you this year?

33:22.160 --> 33:23.440
What month were you born in?
How many people are there in your family?

33:23.440 --> 33:24.510
I am 21 this year,

33:24.540 --> 33:25.640
already at the age of marriage.

33:25.640 --> 33:26.720
Beauty, marry me

33:26.880 --> 33:27.830
and be my bride.

33:27.830 --> 33:29.160
Your Highness!

33:48.830 --> 33:49.550
Doctor,

33:49.880 --> 33:51.280
how are Qiao's injuries?

33:56.640 --> 33:57.790
Young Master,

33:58.030 --> 33:59.000
this lady

33:59.400 --> 34:01.400
has two deep cuts on her right arm.

34:01.790 --> 34:03.750
The one by the elbow is treatable,

34:04.160 --> 34:05.590
but the one on her arm

34:05.920 --> 34:07.580
has hit her veins and tendons.

34:08.030 --> 34:09.230
Even if reconnected,

34:09.800 --> 34:12.400
it's hard to say
whether she can practice martial arts

34:12.400 --> 34:13.320
in the future.

34:14.150 --> 34:14.920
Besides...

34:16.550 --> 34:17.630
Besides what?

34:18.510 --> 34:19.760
It is a little too late

34:19.760 --> 34:21.280
to treat this lady's eyes.

34:21.440 --> 34:22.040
I am afraid

34:22.360 --> 34:24.290
it'll be hard to restore her sight.

34:24.880 --> 34:25.960
Unless...

34:27.159 --> 34:27.960
Unless what?

34:27.989 --> 34:29.400
Can you finish
what you have to say in one go?

34:29.400 --> 34:31.110
Unless you have a potion

34:31.480 --> 34:32.960
called Huotu water.

34:32.960 --> 34:33.710
What water?

34:33.760 --> 34:35.280
Huotu water.

34:36.480 --> 34:37.800
Huotu water?

34:38.280 --> 34:39.110
What's so difficult?

34:39.110 --> 34:40.150
I will send someone to find it.

34:40.150 --> 34:40.920
This medicine

34:40.920 --> 34:43.179
is made from a top-secret prescription.

34:43.510 --> 34:44.920
Few people know about it.

34:45.440 --> 34:46.840
The medicinal materials needed to make it

34:46.840 --> 34:48.110
are also very precious.

34:48.110 --> 34:49.230
Not only that,

34:49.400 --> 34:51.190
the patient needs
to use it for 7 days,

34:51.190 --> 34:52.070
and it must be

34:52.070 --> 34:53.880
freshly prepared every day.

34:54.230 --> 34:55.690
Stop using it after 7 days,

34:55.960 --> 34:57.400
and wait another 7 days,

34:57.670 --> 35:00.360
and then her eyes
will recover on their own.

35:04.320 --> 35:05.720
Thank you, Young Master.

35:13.800 --> 35:14.440
Qiao,

35:14.590 --> 35:15.440
don't worry.

35:15.920 --> 35:17.880
Whatever water, fire, earth, gold, wood—

35:17.880 --> 35:18.960
Biantang is rich in materials.

35:18.960 --> 35:20.090
We have everything.

35:20.590 --> 35:21.590
Come back with me.

35:21.630 --> 35:23.400
I will definitely cure your eyes.

35:23.400 --> 35:24.030
Li Ce,

35:25.750 --> 35:27.060
did you see Zhuge Yue?

35:27.480 --> 35:28.230
Zhuge Yue?

35:29.230 --> 35:30.360
This belongs to him.

35:30.630 --> 35:31.590
He saved me.

35:32.510 --> 35:33.320
Qiao,

35:34.070 --> 35:35.190
do you have a conscience?

35:35.190 --> 35:36.650
I was the one who saved you.

35:36.710 --> 35:38.190
I picked you up from the roadside,

35:38.190 --> 35:39.230
brought you to the inn,

35:39.230 --> 35:40.830
and got a doctor to treat you.

35:41.110 --> 35:42.040
Yet here you are,

35:43.070 --> 35:44.930
talking about Zhuge Yue nonstop.

35:45.150 --> 35:46.070
Without him,

35:46.590 --> 35:47.960
I would have died in the frozen lake.

35:47.960 --> 35:48.440
Without me,

35:48.440 --> 35:50.820
you would have been taken
by Great Yan's soldiers.

35:50.820 --> 35:52.280
If you were caught by them,

35:52.550 --> 35:55.360
you'd wish you were rather dead.

35:55.660 --> 35:57.400
Death by a thousand cuts, cut in half,

35:57.400 --> 35:59.190
skinned, buried alive...

36:09.230 --> 36:09.960
Qiao,

36:10.440 --> 36:11.440
don't overthink.

36:11.950 --> 36:13.500
Curing your eyes is the key.

36:13.840 --> 36:15.150
Great Yan is bitterly cold,

36:15.150 --> 36:16.670
and the doctors' skills are limited.

36:16.670 --> 36:18.150
Come back to Biantang with me.

36:18.150 --> 36:20.070
I'll get the best imperial doctor for you.

36:20.070 --> 36:21.000
I'm not leaving.

36:22.670 --> 36:23.510
Why?

36:23.850 --> 36:25.280
I'm going to wait for Zhuge Yue here.

36:25.280 --> 36:25.800
You...

36:27.600 --> 36:28.600
Zhuge Yue.

36:29.590 --> 36:32.110
Zhuge Yue, Zhuge Yue, Zhuge Yue.

36:33.710 --> 36:34.360
Qiao.

36:34.670 --> 36:35.960
You haven't changed at all.

36:35.960 --> 36:37.280
Once you make up your mind,

36:37.280 --> 36:38.740
you're still sd stubborn.

36:39.800 --> 36:40.480
But,

36:40.800 --> 36:42.030
I like you this way.

36:56.130 --> 36:59.390
♪ We mock karma ♪

36:59.930 --> 37:02.640
♪ For being unfair ♪

37:02.870 --> 37:04.640
♪ Why is life ♪

37:05.110 --> 37:09.200
♪ Often filled with regrets? ♪

37:10.790 --> 37:13.290
♪ The snow falls ♪

37:13.830 --> 37:17.390
♪ With fate ♪

37:17.650 --> 37:18.890
♪ It will eventually ♪

37:19.690 --> 37:21.530
♪ Fall before ♪

37:21.560 --> 37:23.980
♪ The dawn ♪

37:24.410 --> 37:26.680
♪ As a foreigner ♪

37:26.980 --> 37:31.170
♪ Don't look, don't ask, and don't speak ♪

37:31.760 --> 37:34.130
♪ Wander ♪

37:34.160 --> 37:38.690
♪ With no resentment at all ♪

37:38.880 --> 37:41.130
♪ The lock in my heart ♪

37:41.380 --> 37:42.680
♪ Put the memories ♪

37:42.700 --> 37:46.390
♪ In the silence of the night ♪

37:47.120 --> 37:48.620
♪ Look ♪

37:48.780 --> 37:52.750
♪ The mortal world has forgotten me ♪

37:54.440 --> 37:55.580
♪ I wish ♪

37:56.290 --> 38:05.610
♪ You'll forget me ♪

38:01.590 --> 38:02.360
Li Ce.

38:06.670 --> 38:07.670
Is that you?

38:13.400 --> 38:15.200
Could you get me a glass of water?

38:41.190 --> 38:42.110
What's wrong?

39:03.030 --> 39:03.760
Li Ce.

39:04.480 --> 39:06.210
You talk so much during the day.

39:06.480 --> 39:08.710
Why do you say nothing at night?

39:09.630 --> 39:10.320
Also,

39:10.810 --> 39:13.810
what are you doing in my room
in the middle of the night?

39:17.920 --> 39:18.550
Li Ce?

39:20.280 --> 39:20.960
Li Ce?

39:49.440 --> 39:50.550
I know it's you,

39:50.840 --> 39:51.840
Zhuge Yue.

39:51.920 --> 39:53.400
You are a grown man,

39:53.540 --> 39:54.730
yet so indecisive.

39:54.760 --> 39:56.110
If you want to reunite with her,

39:56.110 --> 39:57.040
just go up to her.

39:57.280 --> 39:58.440
Qiao is not stupid.

39:58.710 --> 40:01.110
How could she not sense
you're still alive?

40:01.320 --> 40:02.720
It is already the 6th day.

40:03.190 --> 40:04.320
How are you feeling?

40:05.230 --> 40:06.360
Who exactly are you?

40:06.590 --> 40:08.450
Why are you giving me Huotu water?

40:08.900 --> 40:10.290
Zhuge Yue

40:10.530 --> 40:11.680
is dead.
